KEINEMOD-EPHEMERALITY_POWER.description:
After applied, if the enemy's Ephemerality is exactly:
[blue]1[/blue], enemy gains [blue]1[/blue] [gold]Weak[/gold];
[blue]3[/blue], enemy loses [blue]3[/blue] [gold]Strength[/gold];
[blue]7[/blue], enemy gains [blue]137[/blue] [gold]Disintegration[/gold].

